WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:00.833
Mom

2
00:00:03.700 --> 00:00:04.300
Zhi Han

3
00:00:04.566 --> 00:00:05.133
Come with Mom

4
00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:07.066
No, I want to stay with Dad.

5
00:00:07.233 --> 00:00:07.900
Be good, Zhi Han

6
00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:09.000
Will you come home with Mom?

7
00:00:09.066 --> 00:00:09.566
No.

8
00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:11.700
Zhi Han,

9
00:00:12.033 --> 00:00:12.666
Stop being naughty.

10
00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:13.466
Be good.

11
00:00:14.266 --> 00:00:15.033
Zhang Wen Xu,

12
00:00:15.966 --> 00:00:17.100
What did you say to Zhi Han?

13
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.666
Don't you find this disgusting?

14
00:00:18.666 --> 00:00:19.633
What did I say?

15
00:00:19.966 --> 00:00:21.066
Don't misunderstand me.

16
00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:22.166
Come here, Zhi Han.

17
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:23.666
Come home with Mom.

18
00:00:24.066 --> 00:00:25.433
If not, Mom will be very sad.

19
00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:26.300
No,

20
00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:27.700
You're a bad mom.

21
00:00:27.966 --> 00:00:29.233
You don't want Dad anymore.

22
00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:31.066
And you don't want Zhi Han to see Dad.

23
00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:32.833
You're a bad mom.

24
00:00:36.466 --> 00:00:37.000
That's not true.

25
00:00:38.866 --> 00:00:40.433
Mom just wants to protect you.

26
00:00:41.066 --> 00:00:42.933
So you and Dad got divorced, right?

27
00:00:46.666 --> 00:00:47.000
Yes.

28
00:00:47.366 --> 00:00:48.733
You're a bad mom.

29
00:00:49.166 --> 00:00:50.233
I hate you.

30
00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:53.733
Zhi Han.

31
00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:55.500
See,

32
00:00:56.033 --> 00:00:57.666
It's not me stopping Zhi Han from going.

33
00:00:57.666 --> 00:00:59.466
Zhi Han just doesn't want to go.

34
00:00:59.666 --> 00:01:00.666
Zhang Wen Xu,

35
00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:02.933
What do you want to do?

36
00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.333
Why are you so angry?

37
00:01:04.333 --> 00:01:04.766
Jian Dao,

38
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:06.133
I'm helping you.

39
00:01:06.366 --> 00:01:07.466
Do you know at kindergarten,

40
00:01:07.466 --> 00:01:08.933
Zhi Han was bullied by other kids?

41
00:01:09.033 --> 00:01:10.933
When I picked him up tonight,

42
00:01:10.933 --> 00:01:12.866
He was being bullied by two other kids.

43
00:01:12.866 --> 00:01:14.200
Do you know why?

44
00:01:14.500 --> 00:01:15.833
Because you divorced me.

45
00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.333
You made Zhi Han lose his dad.

46
00:01:20.033 --> 00:01:22.300
Now everyone is calling him an illegitimate child.
